A Dupont-area artist and former lawyer wrote an op-ed in the Washington PostÂ over the weekend that called for the decriminalization of student-teacher relationships in most circumstances. Betsy Karasik's piece was pegged to the high-profile case in Montana, in which a teenage girl had a sexual relationship with her teacher and later committed suicide. The teacher [...]">

