		<li class="flagged-away alt" id="comment-1118549">
						<div class="comment_header">
			  <cite class="comment_author">Charles</cite>
			  <small class="comment_metadata">
			    <a href="#comment-1118549" title="">
			    September 4th, 2013<br/>
