  						</div>
			
			<div class="comment_number">#9</div>
			
			<div class="comment_body">
			 
			  
  			<p>She's still an idiot.</p>
				
									
										<div class="flag-comment"><a href="http://www.washingtoncitypaper.com/blogs/citydesk/2013/09/04/post-op-ed-writer-says-her-message-on-student-teacher-relationships-was-distorted/?_wpnonce=0d1d0f16b6&flagged-comment=1&flagged-comment-id=1118553#comment-1118553">Flag this comment</a></div>					<div style="clear: left"></div>
										<div class="flagged">
						This comment has been flagged.
					</div>
															
							
